						"displayName": "Tony Lukasavage",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "America/Los_Angeles"
					},
					"body": "Thanks guys! I'm going to resolve this issue to take care of the regression, but I'll log a new ticket for more cleanly populating the assets throughout the rest of the platform-specific folders.",
